translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,1,"Bayakubuza ngezimpango zempi ithi, â€œizimpango zingezikaMvelinqangi nesithunywa ngakho-ke sabani uMvelinqangi bese nilungisa lokho okuphakathi kwenu (ukungezwani) futhi nihloniphe uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe uma kungukuthi nina ningabakholwayo"
  8,2,Kuphela abakholwayo yilabo uma kukhulunywa ngoMvelinqangi izinhliziyo zabo zigcwala ukwesaba futhi uma befundelwa amavesi akhe kuyenyukela kubona ukukholwa futhi babeka ithemba eNkosini yabo
  8,3,Labo abenza imithandazo futhi nakulokho esibabele kona bakusebenzise (banikele ngakho)
  8,4,Labo-ke bangamakholwa eqiniso okwabo amazinga (aphezulu) eNkosini yabo nentethelelo nesabelo esihloniphekile
  8,5,Njengoba iNkosi yakho yakukhipha endlini yakho ngeqiniso futhi ngempela iqembu kwabakholwayo lalingakuthandi lokho
  8,6,Bayakuphikisa mayelana neqiniso emva kokuba selicacisiwe kungathi badudulelwa ekufeni (kulapho) bona bekubona
  8,7,Futhi ngenkathi uMvelinqangi enethembisa elinye lamaqembu amabili (elihlomile nelingahlomile) ukuthi lona libe ngelenu nafisa ukuthi lelo elalingahlomile kube ngelenu kepha uMvelinqangi uthanda ukumisa iqiniso ngamazwi akhe bese enqamula izimpande (amasu) abangakholwayo
  8,8,Ukuze amise iqiniso abhuntshise amanga yize noma ngabe abayizoni bekuzonda lokho